<tr><td bgcolor="#D0FFD0" colspan ="2"><b> Changed: </b></td></tr>
<tr><td bgcolor="#FF4040" valign="top" width="1%">&lt;<br />&lt;</td><td><p />
<h2><a name ="Form_Template_Elements"> </a> Form Template Elements </h2>
</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#40FF40" valign="top" width="1%">&gt;<br />&gt;</td><td>
<p />
<h2><a name ="Defining_a_Form_Template"> </a> Defining a Form Template </h2>
<p />
A Form Template is simply a page containing your form, defined in a table where each row is one form field.
<p />
<h3><a name ="Form_Template_Elements"> </a> Form Template Elements </h3>
</td></tr>
<tr><td bgcolor="#D0FFD0" colspan ="2"><b> Changed: </b></td></tr>
<tr><td bgcolor="#FF4040" valign="top" width="1%">&lt;<br />&lt;</td><td><p />
<h3><a name ="Defining_a_Form_Template"> </a> Defining a Form Template </h3>
<p />
A Form Template is simply a page containing your form, defined in a table where each row is one form field.
</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#40FF40" valign="top" width="1%">&gt;<br />&gt;</td><td>
<p />
<h3><a name ="Defining_a_Form_in_One_Topic"> </a> Defining a Form in One Topic </h3>
</td></tr>
<tr><td bgcolor="#FFD7D7" colspan ="2"><b> Deleted: </b></td></tr>
