<ul >
<li> other than checkboxes: <code>name</code>, ex: <code>?BugPriority=1</code>
</li>
<li> checkbox: <code>namevalue=1</code>, ex: <code>?ColourRed=1</code>. <br> Boxes with a tick must be specified.
</li>
</ul>
