<p />
The <code><b>WEBFORMS</b></code> variable in <A HREF="/TWiki/WebPreferences">WebPreferences</A> is optional and defines a list of possible form templates e.g.
</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#40FF40" valign="top" width="1%">&gt;<br />&gt;</td><td>
<p />
Forms are enabled on a per web basis. The <code><b>WEBFORMS</b></code> variable in <A HREF="/TWiki/WebPreferences">WebPreferences</A> is optional and defines a list of possible form templates e.g.
</td></tr>
