</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#40FF40" valign="top" width="1%">&gt;<br />&gt;</td><td>
<p />
A default form template (i.e. new topics get this default form) can be provided by creating the <code><b>WebTopicEditTemplate</b></code> topic in a Web and adding a form to it.  Initial form values can be set here.  
